response.original_title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 3 ~ Blue Justice VII ~
response.overview: On October 21, 2017, Togane Arena in Togane, Chiba hosted NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017 - Day 3 ~ Blue Justice VII, broadcast on NJPWWorld.com. The main event featured Yuji Nagata vs Manabu Nakanishi (17:47). The card also featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI, EVIL, Hiromu Takahashi, SANADA & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Gedo, Kazuchika Okada, SHO & Tomohiro Ishii) (12:00). Other wrestlers on the show include Leo Tonga, Yujiro Takahashi, El Desperado, Taichi, Yoshinobu Kanemaru, Ren Narita, Shota Umino, Tetsuhiro Yagi, Dragon Lee, Jushin Thunder Liger, Tiger Mask, Titus, Hirooki Goto, Toru Yano, YOSHI-HASHI, Minoru Suzuki, TAKA Michinoku, Takashi Iizuka, Hiroyoshi Tenzan, Satoshi Kojima, David Finlay, Juice Robinson, Kota Ibushi and more!
